high_descs: Turn around, and go to the left in front of the couch to find the round coffee table.
Pick up the keys from the coffee table.
Take the keys and move a few steps to the right so the coffee table is still in front.
Put the keys inside the box on the coffee table.
Pick up the box from the coffee table.
Take the box, and move to the left just slightly around the table.
Place the box on the right side of the couch in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Put keys inside a box and move it to the couch.

high_descs: Walk to the round table
Pick the keys up from the table
Take the keys and place them in to the box that is on the round table
Pick the box up from the table
Carry the box around the living room
Walk over to the couch
Set the box down that has the keys in it
anns.task_desc: Gather they keys and put them in the box

high_descs: Turn right, go straight, turn right before the couch, go straight, turn left and go straight to the coffee table.
Take the keys from the coffee table.
Go to the side of the coffee table closer to the TV and face the coffee table.
Put the keys in the box on the coffee table.
Take the box from the coffee table.
Go around the coffee table to the left to the two seat couch ahead.
Put the box on the right seat of the couch.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with keys in it on a couch.

high_descs: Turn around and walk passed the couch toward the round grey coffee table.
Pick up the keys from the coffee table.
Turn to your right and walk around to other side of the stool next to you and approach the coffee table again.
Place the keys in the box sitting on the coffee table.
Pick up the box with the keys inside.
Walk back around the coffee table toward the grey sofa and stand in front of it.
Place the box on the right side of the grey sofa in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Get keys from coffee table, put them in the box on the table and place box on sofa.

high_descs: Turn around and then walk left until you are at a coffee table
Pick up the keys off of the table
Turn right and then turn to your left twice so that you are facing the table again
Drop the keys into the empty cardboard box on the table
Pick up the cardboard box off of the table
Turn left then walk right, turn right again and then face to your left so you are looking at the sofa
Place the cardboard box on the right cushion of the sofa
anns.task_desc: Place a cardboard box with keys in it on the sofa
